
Features:

two categories of users
    regular players get emails earlier
    normal players receive emails later

give reason when un-subscribing

mass communication/announcements
    ability to send emails to all players for a given game

suspend receiving email

Technical tasks:

    spork or rerun - something to run test on change (replace spork with either zeus or spring)
    indexes
    foreign keys
    continuous delivery - free ruby CI
    performance tests - https://github.com/rails/rails-perftest
